{"tid":1063916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨家】李東海小學校長疑不堪壓力 入住沙田醫院精神科病房","createTime":"2019-03-16T06:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T06:58:25.000Z","uid":29540,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"12505d34e86894ee6844ce122ea3d6a0b6abec02","tid":1063916,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190316&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59375361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190316%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59375361&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnBT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=bb28d35d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190316%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59375361&h=a7c0d8f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190316&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59375361</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍東華三院李東海小學女教師疑不堪壓力，上周三（6日）在校內墮樓身亡，後來被校內其他教師揭發死者生前屢遭校長羅婉儀壓迫，事發前一日更被召到校長室責罵，被勒令要重寫「悔過書」。事件曝光後，輿論矛頭指向羅婉儀校長，羅一直沒有公開回應事件，並於周日（10日）起向校方請假。消息指，備受批評的羅婉儀，懷疑不堪壓力，日前到威爾斯親王醫院急症室求診，再被轉介到沙田醫院精神科，目前入住該院精神科病房。<br />\n<br />\n記者今早到過沙田醫院精神科病房擬探望羅校長，病房護士先查問記者是否在病人的探病名單內，該名單只列有羅婉儀的親人名字，其後另一名護士聽到記者是前來探羅婉儀後，即改口稱病房內並無此病人，並着記者離開。病房內有一名方型臉戴眼鏡的中年女病人，戴着口罩半臥在病床上看雜誌，但記者未能確認她是否羅婉儀。<br />\n<br />\n女教師墮樓事件曝光後，羅婉儀一直未有露面回應及解釋，並隨即休假，東華三院會成立獨立調查委員會處理事件，隨後羅的facebook個人帳戶工作狀態亦改為李東海小學的「前任女校長」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n校長做乜係度扮病扮可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33024f727989cb14a48928fc5f10103161e2de01","tid":1063916,"uid":162954,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"死八婆想扮痴線當無事"},{"pid":"149fb8ba5b2cb47466539ae0fd38086af18c9d65","tid":1063916,"uid":128223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b4d7ce3ad5dc6ff50a279ebb4485ec1f76093ba","tid":1063916,"uid":208376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"頂唔順你點解唔去跳樓反而要浪費香港醫療資源"},{"pid":"661e07cd56b4d3325924b65c7c37225a256f362e","tid":1063916,"uid":12267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"扮傻攞白卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191430d53396e69b1646d6b929e9d9d3d9fc795d","tid":1063916,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"病喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係時間叫佢返學校寫悔過書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7ff3b62464ff514ea108b8cc873e03e4e62954","tid":1063916,"uid":133130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"希望佢真係癡左線"},{"pid":"1a2961bc669d3d5779fb7628111ebe9d1421dc5f","tid":1063916,"uid":6291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"其實佢本身都癡癡地啦<br />\n不過又唔係蠢 而家就識去攞白卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2784f8d383e48646fe8c6148e71aceeed295bb","tid":1063916,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0335f4ee379d56c395cba9058866f11ac2be43","tid":1063916,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:58:25.000Z","msg":"識玩<br />\n知道自己有機會係刑事<br />\n拎定白卡先"}]}